{"word":"εἷμα","slug":"εἷμα","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>εἷμα</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:ἕννυμι'><el>ἕννυμι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>a garment</i>, in <a href='S:plural'>pl.</a> <i>clothes, clothing</i>, <b><a href='S:Homer'>Hom.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><i>a cover, rug, carpet</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}